      "content": "hey so im a student in berlin and things are super stressful right now with finals coming up. im currently on sertraline for my depression but i feel like it's not really doing enough to help with the anxiety/mood swings lately. i was thinking about adding st johns wort to my routine to help boost my mood naturally since it's herbal. is it okay to take both together? or is there any issue with adding it?",
